Deepsleep Silk 1000 Mattress
products.description: The DeepSleep Silk 1000 Mattress offers the perfect balance of comfort, support, and year-round versatility. Featuring Dual Season technology, it provides a cooler sleeping surface for summer and a warmer, cosier feel for wintersimply flip it to suit the season. At its core, 1000 individually responsive pocket springs move independently to deliver tailored support where your body needs it most, reducing partner disturbance and promoting proper spinal alignment. A layer of contouring memory foam relieves pressure points and minimises tossing and turning, ensuring deep, uninterrupted sleep. Wrapped in a soft, breathable luxury knit fabric that enhances airflow, the mattress is finished with deep hand tufting to secure the fillings in placeoffering both an elegant look and long-lasting comfort.

products.title: Deepsleep Camberley Mattress
products.description: The Deepsleep Camberley Antibacterial Mattress delivers reliable support and breathable comfort, making it an excellent all-rounder. Featuring a durable Bonnell spring system and allergy-free, breathable fillings , it provides a consistent medium feel suitable for most sleepers. This double-sided mattress is designed for even wear  simply flip and rotate to maintain shape over time. The microquilted flat top ensures a smooth, level sleeping surface, while the soft Tencel knit fabric cover enhances breathability, moisture control, and overall comfort . Air vents promote temperature regulation and airflow , keeping the mattress cool and hygienic throughout the night. Made with hypoallergenic materials , it creates a cleaner sleep environment, ideal for those with sensitivities. Finished with flag-stitched handles for easy manoeuvrability, the Deepsleep Camberley Antibacterial Mattress offers supportive, breathable, and comfortable sleep at great value.

products.title: Deepsleep Eclipse Ortho Mattress
products.description: The Deepsleep Eclipse Ortho Mattress delivers firm, orthopaedic support and long-lasting comfort. Built with a durable 12.5-gauge Bonnell spring system, it offers reliable back support and a sturdier feelperfect for those who prefer a firmer sleeping surface. Deep layers of luxury comfort fillings provide cushioning without compromising support, while the Flexi Edge system reinforces the sides for full edge-to-edge stability, reducing roll-off and maximising sleeping space. Wrapped in a breathable, soft-touch knitted fabric and finished with a micro-quilted surface for durability, this mattress promotes airflow and helps regulate body temperature throughout the night. Reversible by design, it should be turned regularly to extend its life. Proudly made in the UK by an NBF-approved manufacturer, the Eclipse Ortho combines quality craftsmanship with exceptional everyday value.

products.title: Deepsleep Luxury Pocket 1000 Mattress
products.description: Experience exceptional support and indulgent comfort with the Deepsleep Luxury Pocket 1000 Mattress . Crafted in the UK by a trusted National Bed Federation (NBF) member , it blends premium materials and intelligent design for a truly restful nights sleep. At its heart, 1000 pocket springs respond independently to your body, offering tailored support , pressure relief , and minimising partner disturbance. Luxury comfort fillings and a cashmere knit super soft fabric cover create a plush, breathable surface that enhances sleep quality. An edge-to-edge support system reinforces the perimeter, maximising usable sleeping space and preventing roll-off. Ideal for those seeking durable support with a touch of luxury, the Deepsleep Luxury Pocket 1000 Mattress comes in all UK standard sizes, from small single to super king, and includes a 12-month guarantee . Approximate depth: 26cm / 10 inches . Reversible for easy care and long-lasting comfort.

products.title: Deepsleep Visco Comfort Divan Bed
products.description: Experience enhanced comfort and reliable support with the Deepsleep Visco Comfort Divan Bed  expertly designed to blend traditional spring support with modern memory foam cushioning. The Visco Comfort Mattress features a durable Bonnell spring unit that provides balanced support across the entire sleeping surface, while a layer of contouring memory foam adapts to your bodys shape, easing pressure points and helping to reduce aches and pains. Soft comfort fillings and a micro-quilted surface deliver a plush, uniform feel, while the breathable knitted fabric cover promotes airflow for a cooler nights sleep. Designed with convenience in mind, this non-turn mattress only requires rotation from head to toe to maintain its comfort and longevity. The supportive divan base complements the mattress perfectly and is available with optional storage drawers to keep your bedroom organised. Proudly made in the UK to the highest standards, the Deepsleep Visco Comfort Divan Bed combines everyday comfort, long-lasting support, and timeless style  making it the perfect choice for a restful nights sleep.

products.title: Gilt Edge Bliss Comfort 1000 Mattress
products.description: The Bliss Comfort 1000 Mattress is designed for those who love a plush, gentle sleeping surface with reliable support. With a medium soft comfort rating and a deep cushioning top layer, this mattress provides a sumptuous, cloud-like feel  ideal for side sleepers or anyone who enjoys sinking into their mattress at the end of the day. At the heart of the mattress lies 1000 individually pocketed springs (based on king size), which respond independently to your bodys shape and weight. This helps deliver personalised, zoned support while reducing motion transfer, making it perfect for couples. The mattress features flexi edge support for added stability and a deeper, usable sleep surface. The deep hand-tufted finish secures the internal layers, ensuring long-term structure and performance, while air vents promote breathability for a cooler, fresher nights sleep. Upholstered in a luxury knitted fabric and made in the UK, the Bliss Comfort 1000 Mattress is backed by a 5 Year Warranty , offering long-lasting reassurance and excellent value for money. A non-turn design means simple care  just rotate regularly to keep it in top condition.

Designed for those who want pressure relief without overheating, this mattress adapts perfectly to your body while maintaining breathability for a refreshing night's sleep.

products.title: Gilt Edge Gel Hybrid 1000 Adapt Mattress
products.description: The Adapt 1000 Mattress combines advanced technology and luxurious comfort to provide a truly restful sleep experience. Featuring 1000 luxury pocket springs, this premium support system offers no motion transfer, ensuring that your sleep remains undisturbed, even if your partner moves during the night. The gel foam core provides additional support for your lower back and neck, adapting to your bodys contours while delivering bounce and quick recovery. A foam-encapsulated border provides edge-to-edge support, maximising your sleeping area, and the luxury knitted cover offers a soft and sumptuous surface for added comfort. Designed with airflow in mind, air vents help reduce moisture build-up, keeping the mattress fresh. It's also single-sided for easy maintenancejust rotate regularly.

products.title: Gilt Edge Gel Revive 1500 Divan Bed
products.description: The Revive 1500 mattress is designed to deliver advanced support, pressure relief, and luxurious comfort for a refreshing nights sleep. At its core are 1500 luxury pocket springs, each operating independently to provide targeted, motion-free support. This premium spring system adapts to your bodys contours, offering zoned comfort and reducing movement transfer between sleeping partners. The mattress features a gel foam core that delivers additional support for key pressure points such as the lower back and neck. The gel-infused foam not only adds resilience and bounce to the mattress but also helps it recover its shape quickly, ensuring lasting comfort and durability. Its ideal for those who want the contouring benefits of foam without feeling stuck or overheated. Encased in a luxury knitted cover, the Revive 1500 provides a soft and breathable sleep surface that enhances your overall comfort. Air vents are built into the sides of the mattress to improve airflow and help regulate temperature, keeping the mattress fresh night after night. This mattress offers a perfect balance of support and convenience. The Revive 1500 is the ideal choice for sleepers seeking a harmonious blend of cushioning, support, and temperature control.

products.title: Gilt Edge Latex Cloud 2000 Divan Bed
products.description: The Gilt Edge Latex Cloud 2000 Divan Bed combines luxurious comfort, advanced support, and practical storage options. Its mattress features 2000 firm and supportive pocket springs, each responding independently to your bodys movements for precise, contoured comfort. This helps reduce partner disturbance and ensures a peaceful nights rest. The innovative Coolatex layer offers breathable, responsive latex comfort that relieves pressure while keeping you cool throughout the night. A soft-touch luxury knit fabric cover completes the premium feel and look. With Flexi Edge support to reinforce the mattress edges, youll enjoy an enhanced sleeping surface without the rolling off sensation. The hand-tufted finish ensures long-lasting durability, while the dual season design allows the mattress to be flipped to suit warmer or cooler months. Its reversible construction extends its lifespan, and the medium-firm comfort rating provides the perfect balance between cushioning and support. The divan base is crafted from solid hardwood timber for strength and durability, with a sturdy platform top to support the mattress perfectly. Available in a wide choice of fabrics and colours, the base includes chrome glides, ideal for both carpet and hard flooring. Storage options are available, including various drawer configurations to suit your needs.

products.description: Discover superior orthopaedic support and luxurious comfort with the Gilt Edge Ultra Ortho 2000 Ottoman Bed Set , complete with mattress and your choice of 24-inch or 54-inch headboard . The Ultra Ortho 2000 mattress features 2000 individual pocket springs that deliver precise, targeted support to every part of your body. This helps reduce pressure points and promotes healthy spinal alignment for a restorative nights sleep. A firm white fibre blend comfort layer adds extra support while maintaining a gentle cushioning effect. Edge-to-edge support maximises the usable sleeping surface and ensures stability across the entire bed. The ottoman base is crafted from a robust wooden frame with a sprung platform, enhancing mattress support and evenly distributing weight. Upholstered in durable fabric with elegant deep button-tufting, this bed combines style, strength, and practicality. Available in all standard UK sizes, this divan bed set is perfect for those seeking firm orthopaedic support, ample storage, and lasting durability without compromising comfort.
